Class JSTextFileUtility

java.lang.Object
  js.JSTextFileUtility

public class JSTextFileUtility
extends java.lang.Object

JSTextFileUtility is a class which provides simple read/write access to a plain text file stored on disk.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Josh

appendToFileWithSeparator

public boolean appendToFileWithSeparator(java.lang.String stringToAppend,
                                         java.lang.String separator)
Appends the specified text to the end of this JSTextFileUtility's file, after adding the specified separator.

Usually the separator will be either a space or a new line, so these are provided as JSTextFileUtility.SPACE and JSTextFileUtility.NEW_LINE for more readable code.

Parameters:
stringToAppend - the text to append to the file
separator - a string that is added to the file between the current contents and the new text
Returns:
true if the operation was successful; false otherwise.
